{"tid":1966112,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"尋hku cindy 158身高的典型雙魚座","createTime":"2020-04-10T03:18:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-18T12:03:47.000Z","uid":52173,"like":1,"dislike":50,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"1b7237e97369b83a8931fbb0b33d66c21d4d44f3","tid":1966112,"uid":52173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T03:18:36.000Z","msg":"之前12月時識得一位絲打CD rom<br />\n但我蠢講左d 令你唔開心既說話<br />\n眼見宜家武漢肺炎咁嚴重<br />\n覺得生命可貴同唔想後悔<br />\n唔知幾時會有人中招同離開<br />\n所以想親自向你講聲對唔住<br />\n唔知係呢到有無機會搵得返你呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n叫Cindy 讀緊HKU 158身高 雙魚座 <br />\n因為記得佢果科比較特別<br />\n加上擔心呢段時間佢仲要出去實習<br />\n早排幫你係網上訂左d 口罩 ASTM lv2 <br />\n希望幫到你同屋企人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果你唔介意我呢個蠢朋友<br />\n可以加返我TG<br />\n因為記得你講過會係連登睇感情台同故事台d post<br />\n所以想係係呢到開post搵返你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/Frankie9705\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FFrankie9705&d=GkP5J4C4AUyWsqXHyTPi6xTmJET03dBbukdTSFliYCA%3D&h=f7e7db64\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/Frankie9705</a>"},{"pid":"d64d4583c63b33e6117bc4b81b47331eb4b29327","tid":1966112,"uid":87498,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T03:59:20.000Z","msg":"原來你就係果條柒頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d5a7278a48df3577118fcfe6892838eb2eb5783","tid":1966112,"uid":54719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T04:01:40.000Z","msg":"唔理真還是假<br />\n但你個tg名太有指向性......<br />\nmon po狗好易推論到你係邊個<br />\n快啲轉名啦樓豬"},{"pid":"ad70c6592165caea56077bc837a73acddf80d0ce","tid":1966112,"uid":52173,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"9d5a7278a48df3577118fcfe6892838eb2eb5783","tid":1966112,"uid":54719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T04:01:40.000Z","msg":"唔理真還是假<br />\n但你個tg名太有指向性......<br />\nmon po狗好易推論到你係邊個<br />\n快啲轉名啦樓豬"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10